{"tid":1585090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動建議】10月1號齊來賀國慶","createTime":"2019-09-21T12:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T15:27:14.000Z","uid":67232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fba5f31afb6f7b517b5b777aaae3f6f505d0b260","tid":1585090,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"偉大嘅祖國生日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作為愛國愛黨嘅連登仔，緊係唔可以少得嗰日嘅慶祝活動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個月前班黃尸喺85搞嗰D分區集會咁多人咁轟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今次到我哋主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋去返佢哋上次85集會嘅地方支持祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有模有樣咁學佢哋搞翻個分區賀國慶集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗麻煩到港鐵要佢哋封站，交通方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />街坊派禮物比我哋又方便D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然無不反對通知書就唔好出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />犯法架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋藍絲連登仔奉公守法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是護旗手🇺🇲🇺🇲🇺🇲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58d852d5f130a65dde4d2c7419fb6c506e302af","tid":1585090,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span styl